author: RTÉ News
title: Sydney police take 'black box' off cruise ship
description: Australian police has said they have taken the "black box" of a cruise ship which disembarked hundreds of passengers infected with the coronavirus in Sydney, as part of a homicide investigation into the country's deadliest infection source.
